				{
					"type": "thinking_start"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "The user is asking me to write a paragraph about automated testing and software quality. This is a straightforward writing request -",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " not a coding task. I can respond directly without using any tools.",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_stop"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "Automated testing is important for software quality because it provides fast, repeatable verification that code",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " behaves as expected after every change. Manual testing is slow, error-prone, and doesn't scale —",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " humans miss edge cases, forget to re-check regressions, and can't feas",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "ibly re-run hundreds of scenarios on every commit.",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " Automated tests catch regressions early, when they're cheapest to fix, and serve as executable documentation of intended behavior. They enable confident",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " refactoring by providing a safety net that immediately flags unintended side effects. In CI",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "/CD workflows, automated tests act as a gate that prevents broken code from reaching production, reducing incident rates",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " and the cost of defects. Over time, a well",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "-maintained test suite compounds in value: it encodes institutional knowledge about",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " known bugs and edge cases, making the codebase more resilient as",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " it grows and as team members change.",
					"messageId": "msg_d28fc9076001fD1tT0c6viF1cH"
				},
